## Step 5: Edit App.java

Open:

```bash
vim src/main/java/com/example/App.java
```

Press:

```
i   (to enter insert mode)
```

Delete everything and paste:

```java
package com.example;

public class App {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        System.out.println("Hello Gradle World!");

        Calculator calc = new Calculator();

        System.out.println("Addition: 15 + 25 = " + calc.add(15, 25));
        System.out.println("Subtraction: 50 - 20 = " + calc.subtract(50, 20));
        System.out.println("Multiplication: 7 * 8 = " + calc.multiply(7, 8));
        System.out.println("Division: 100 / 4 = " + calc.divide(100, 4));
    }
}
```

Save and exit:

```
ESC
:wq
```

