## Step 7: Edit AppTest.java

```bash
vim src/test/java/com/example/AppTest.java
```

Replace everything with:

```java
package com.example;

import junit.framework.Test;
import junit.framework.TestCase;
import junit.framework.TestSuite;

public class AppTest extends TestCase {

    private Calculator calculator;

    public void setUp() {
        calculator = new Calculator();
    }

    public void testAdd() {
        assertEquals(40, calculator.add(15, 25));
        assertEquals(0, calculator.add(-5, 5));
    }

    public void testSubtract() {
        assertEquals(30, calculator.subtract(50, 20));
        assertEquals(-10, calculator.subtract(5, 15));
    }

    public void testMultiply() {
        assertEquals(56, calculator.multiply(7, 8));
        assertEquals(0, calculator.multiply(10, 0));
    }

    public void testDivide() {
        assertEquals(25.0, calculator.divide(100, 4), 0.01);
        assertEquals(2.5, calculator.divide(5, 2), 0.01);
    }

    public void testDivideByZero() {
        try {
            calculator.divide(10, 0);
            fail("Expected IllegalArgumentException");
        } catch (IllegalArgumentException e) {
            assertTrue(true);
        }
    }
}
```

Save:

```
ESC
:wq
```

