# PART B: Convert to Gradle

---

## Step 13: Convert project

```bash
gradle init
```

Select:

```
yes
1 (Kotlin DSL)
yes
```

---

## Step 14: Open Gradle file

```bash
vim build.gradle.kts
```

Replace content with:

```kotlin
plugins {
    java
    application
}

repositories {
    mavenCentral()
}

dependencies {
    testImplementation("junit:junit:4.13.2")
}

application {
    mainClass.set("com.example.App")
}
```

Save.

---

## Step 15: Build project

```bash
gradle build
```

---

## Step 16: Run project

```bash
gradle run
```

You will get same output.

---

